JOBSHEET KAYANYA
# 1. SETTING IP ADDRESS VM

Edit konfigurasi IP:

```bash
nano /etc/netplan/00-installer-config.yml
```

➡️ Mengatur IP statis Ubuntu.

Terapkan konfigurasi:

```bash
netplan apply
```

➡️ Mengaktifkan konfigurasi IP yang baru.

Cek IP:

```bash
ip a
```

➡️ Melihat IP Address yang aktif.

Tes koneksi:

```bash
ping 192.168.1.20
```

➡️ Memastikan VM1 dan VM2 saling terhubung.

---

# 2. INSTALL GIT DAN CLONE REPOSITORY

Install Git:

```bash
apt update
apt install git -y
```

➡️ Menginstall Git.

Clone repository:

```bash
git clone <url-github>
```

➡️ Mengambil source code Laravel dari GitHub.

Masuk ke project:

```bash
cd adit-22-laravel
```

➡️ Masuk ke folder project.

Cek isi folder:

```bash
ls
```

➡️ Memastikan file project sudah ada.

---

# 3. MEMBUAT FILE .ENV

Masuk ke folder Laravel:

```bash
cd laravel-app
```

➡️ Masuk ke source Laravel.

Copy env:

```bash
cp .env.example .env
```

➡️ Membuat file konfigurasi Laravel.

Edit env:

```bash
nano .env
```

➡️ Mengubah konfigurasi database.

Contoh:

```env
DB_CONNECTION=mysql
DB_HOST=mysql-adit-22
DB_PORT=3306
DB_DATABASE=adit22_db
DB_USERNAME=adit22_user
DB_PASSWORD=adit@2026Secure
```

---

# 4. INSTALL DOCKER

Update package:

```bash
apt update
```

➡️ Memperbarui repository Ubuntu.

Install Docker:

```bash
apt install docker.io docker-compose-v2 -y
```

➡️ Menginstall Docker Engine dan Docker Compose.

Aktifkan Docker:

```bash
systemctl enable docker
systemctl start docker
```

➡️ Menjalankan service Docker.

Cek Docker:

```bash
docker -v
```

➡️ Memastikan Docker berhasil terinstall.

---

# 5. BUILD DAN MENJALANKAN CONTAINER

Kembali ke root project:

```bash
cd /adit-22-laravel
```

Build image:

```bash
docker compose build
```

➡️ Membuat image berdasarkan Dockerfile.

Menjalankan container:

```bash
docker compose up -d
```

➡️ Menjalankan seluruh service.

Cek container:

```bash
docker ps
```

➡️ Memastikan container aktif.

Harus muncul:

```text
app-adit-22-1
app-adit-22-2
app-adit-22-3
mysql-adit-22
```

---

# 6. CEK MYSQL

Masuk ke MySQL:

```bash
docker exec -it mysql-adit-22 mysql -u root -p
```

➡️ Login ke MySQL Container.

Lihat database:

```sql
SHOW DATABASES;
```

➡️ Memastikan database berhasil dibuat.

Lihat user:

```sql
SELECT User, Host FROM mysql.user;
```

➡️ Memastikan user database ada.

Keluar:

```sql
exit
```

---

# 7. MASUK KE CONTAINER LARAVEL

Masuk:

```bash
docker exec -it app-adit-22-1 bash
```

➡️ Masuk ke Laravel Container.

Cek Laravel:

```bash
php artisan about
```

➡️ Memastikan Laravel berjalan.

Test database:

```bash
