```

---

# 12. MEMBUAT INVENTORY ANSIBLE

Buat folder:

```bash
mkdir /ansible
cd /ansible
```

➡️ Folder kerja Ansible.

Buat inventory:

```bash
nano inventory.ini
```

Isi:

```ini
[managed]
vm2 ansible_host=192.168.1.20 ansible_user=adit

[managed:vars]
ansible_python_interpreter=/usr/bin/python3
```

➡️ Daftar host yang akan dikelola.

---

# 13. TEST ANSIBLE

Ping:

```bash
ansible -i inventory.ini managed -m ping
```

➡️ Mengecek koneksi Ansible.

Harus muncul:

```text
pong
```

Cek user:

```bash
ansible -i inventory.ini managed -m command -a "whoami"
```

➡️ Menjalankan command di VM2.

---

# 14. INSTALL HAPROXY (VM1)

Install:

```bash
apt install haproxy -y
```

➡️ Menginstall HAProxy.

Cek versi:

```bash
haproxy -v
```

➡️ Memastikan HAProxy terinstall.

---

# 15. KONFIGURASI HAPROXY

Edit:

```bash
nano /etc/haproxy/haproxy.cfg
```

Tambahkan:

```cfg
frontend laravel_frontend
    bind *:80
    mode http
    default_backend laravel_backend

backend laravel_backend
    mode http
    balance roundrobin

    server app1 192.168.1.20:8081 check
    server app2 192.168.1.20:8082 check
    server app3 192.168.1.20:8083 check
```

➡️ Mengatur Load Balancing ke 3 container Laravel.

---

# 16. VALIDASI HAPROXY

Cek syntax:

```bash
haproxy -c -f /etc/haproxy/haproxy.cfg
```

➡️ Memastikan konfigurasi tidak error.

Restart:

```bash
systemctl restart haproxy
```

➡️ Mengaktifkan konfigurasi baru.

Status:

```bash
systemctl status haproxy
```

➡️ Memastikan service berjalan.

---

# 17. TEST LOAD BALANCER

Cek port:

```bash
ss -tulpn | grep :80
```

➡️ Memastikan HAProxy mendengarkan port 80.

Test backend:

```bash
curl -I http://192.168.1.20:8081
curl -I http://192.168.1.20:8082
curl -I http://192.168.1.20:8083
```

➡️ Memastikan semua replica hidup.

Test HAProxy:

```bash
curl -I http://192.168.1.10
```

➡️ Memastikan request masuk ke HAProxy.

Akses browser:

```text
http://192.168.1.10
```

➡️ Web Laravel tampil melalui Load Balancer.

